Grand Lodge Knights of Pythias of Florida, Plaintiff in Error, v. Dennis Taylor, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Duval. 8. D. MoGill, for Plaintiff in Error;

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for plain tiff in error.

No appearance for Defendant in Error.
